  subtitle="<div style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;'>The Omnes Gentes Project (OGP)</span> is a global mission dedicated to bringing the Gospel to the most remote regions, where the message of Christ has never reached and where no Catholic communities exist. We send missionaries with one singular mission: <span style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;'>to win souls for Jesus</span> and to strive to live a life of holiness. <br/><br/>Our purpose is to fulfill Jesus' command to carry the Gospel to all nations, as expressed in:<br/><br/><span style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;'><cite>Go therefore and make disciples of all nations(Omnes Gentes), baptizing them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit.</cite>—Matthew 28:19</span> <br/><br/>This is our calling, our duty, and our joy. Together, we rise to bring the light of Christ to the darkest corners of the earth, for every soul deserves to hear the Good News and experience the saving love of our Lord. Let us be bold, faithful, and unwavering in this divine mission. <span style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;'>For the glory of God and the salvation of souls!</span></div>"
