  { description: "This is the heart of the Omnes Gentes Project: to bring the light of Christ to the darkest places, to plant the seeds of faith where they have never been sown, and to build a legacy of hope, salvation, and eternal life. <span style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;'>For the glory of God and the salvation of souls!<span/>" },
