>
<Fragment slot="content">
<span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-2xl mb-2">HOPE</span> is the spiritual, emotional, and moral strength ingrained in missionaries. It carries them through the challenges of the mission field and aids in overcoming despair. It is the inner light that enables them to persevere in the face of adversity, to cling to God’s promises, and to bring the message of salvation to those who live in darkness. 
</Fragment>
</Content>
<Content
